snippet.title: The True Abusers Of Johnny Depp Exposed: It's Not Just Amber Heard
snippet.description:
In this video we will be aiming to create awareness, enlighten the public about domestic violence against men by discussing the true abusers of Johnny Depp if he is innocent of the allegations placed forth by Amber heart in court against him, and her foing all the way to stand as a witness against his defamation lawsuit with the sun newspaper in the UK,as well as , the fact that domestic violence against men needs to be taken very seriously, the big loss of Amber heard as her pursuit to throw Johnny Depp's case out of court fails, and lastly the devastating effects women who lie about been domestically violated impacts negatively on those who are true abused.
